                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold">Telegram Bot</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-bone-dark opacity-60">Instant ticket creation</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-bone-dark leading-relaxed opacity-80 mb-4">
              Send a message to our bot and it will automatically classify and create a GitHub issue for you.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 rounded border border-accent/30 text-accent bg-accent/10">üêõ Bugs</span>
